OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright spells and showers from the
OL,7,Fwest on Thursday. A further rain band
OL,8,Fpushes northeast on Friday. Bright
OL,9,Fspells and showers again on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
